Everyone starts at level 1. Your level is displayed below your profile photo:


Here's how you gain points:



We unlock features and prizes the higher your level goes. Here's an overview at the modules you'll unlock as you level up:


  • Level 2: You'll be able to DM other members

  • Level 3: You'll get a custom proposal review from me (Nico)

  • Level 4: You'll get a custom profile review from me

  • Level 5: You'll unlock our custom Upwork CRM + Automations

  • Level 7: You'll get free lifetime access to our community!!


You can unlock our custom Upwork CRM + Automations early by attending one of our onboarding calls, which you can find on the calendar.


And if you're curious what level everyone else in the community is at, you can check the leaderboards here:

https://www.skool.com/upwork-outbound/-/leaderboards


P.S. If you make your intro post and engage with other members in the comments section of your post, you can easily get to level 3 or 4 and unlock our proposal and profile reviews.
